            "id": "http://example.com/category/664761ec1ed2.html",
            "url": "http://example.com/category/664761ec1ed2.html",
            "title": "Docker安装LAMP",
            "date_published": "2022-09-11T10:06:45.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"docker基本使用\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#docker基本使用\">#</a> Docker 基本使用</h2>\n<h3 id=\"docker的组成\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#docker的组成\">#</a> Docker 的组成</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>docker 服务器与 docker 客户端</li>\n<li>docker 镜像\n<ul>\n<li>分层</li>\n<li>写时复制</li>\n<li>内容寻址</li>\n<li>联合挂载</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>docker 仓库</li>\n<li>docker 容器</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"仓库与镜像\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#仓库与镜像\">#</a> 仓库与镜像</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>设置国内镜像仓库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 注册阿里云账号，选择镜像仓库加速服务</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 修改文件</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">vim</span> /etc/docker/daemon.json</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token string\">\"registry-mirrors\"</span>:<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://xxxxx.mirror.aliyun.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>搜索镜像</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> search centos</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>下载镜像</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> pull centos</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>查看镜像</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> images</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"创建容器与进入容器\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#创建容器与进入容器\">#</a> 创建容器与进入容器</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>创建第一个容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-itd</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>--name 容器名称<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> 镜像名/ID</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>查看容器列表</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">ps</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">ps</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-a</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>进入这个容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-it</span> 容器名/ID /bin/bash</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"关闭容器和删除容器\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#关闭容器和删除容器\">#</a> 关闭容器和删除容器</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>关闭一个正在运行的容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> stop 容器名/ID</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>删除一个没有运行的容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">rm</span> 容器名/ID</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>杀死一个正在运行的容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">kill</span> 容器名/ID</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"制作离线镜像包\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#制作离线镜像包\">#</a> 制作离线镜像包</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>使用修改过的容器制作新镜像</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> commit 容器ID 镜像名称:新tag</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> save <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-o</span> 离线包名.tar 镜像名:镜像tag</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>查看镜像差异</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">diff</span> 镜像ID</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>保存为离线包</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> save <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-o</span> 离线包名.tar 镜像名:镜像tag</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"导入离线镜像包\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#导入离线镜像包\">#</a> 导入离线镜像包</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>将离线包导入到 docker 镜像中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> load <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-i</span> tar包</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>使用离线镜像创建容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-itd</span> ID</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"暴露端口与目录\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#暴露端口与目录\">#</a> 暴露端口与目录</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>将容器内的端口号暴露到宿主系统</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-itd</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span> 宿主路径:容器内路径  镜像ID</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>将宿主系统的目录挂载到容器中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-itd</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-p</span> 宿主端口号:容器内端口号 镜像ID</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"容器与宿主机数据拷贝\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#容器与宿主机数据拷贝\">#</a> 容器与宿主机数据拷贝</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># docker cp : 用于容器与主机之间的数据拷贝。</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 语法</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># docker cp [OPTIONS] CONTAINER:SRC_PATH DEST_PATH|-</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># docker cp [OPTIONS] SRC_PATH|- CONTAINER:DEST_PATH</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># OPTIONS 说明：</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># -L : 保持源目标中的链接</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 实例</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 将主机 /opt/nginx 目录拷贝到容器 96f7f14e99ab 的 /www 目录下。</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">cp</span> /opt/nginx 96f7f14e99ab:/www/</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 将主机 /opt/nginx 目录拷贝到容器 96f7f14e99ab 中，目录重命名为 www。</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">cp</span> /opt/nginx 96f7f14e99ab:/www</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"14\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 将容器 96f7f14e99ab 的 /www 目录拷贝到主机的 /tmp 目录中。</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"15\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token function\">cp</span>  96f7f14e99ab:/www /tmp/</pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"查看容器日志\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#查看容器日志\">#</a> 查看容器日志</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># docker logs : 获取容器的日志</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 语法</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># docker logs [OPTIONS] CONTAINER</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># OPTIONS 说明：</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># -f : 跟踪日志输出</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># --since : 显示某个开始时间的所有日志</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># -t : 显示时间戳</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># --tail : 仅列出最新 N 条容器日志</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 实例</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 跟踪查看容器 nginx 的日志输出。</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"14\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> logs <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-f</span> nginx</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"15\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"16\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">192.168</span>.239.1 - - <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span>/sep/2022:16:53:33 +0000<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"GET / HTTP/1.1\"</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span> <span class=\"token number\">612</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/45.0.2454.93 Safari/537.36\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-\"</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"17\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">2022</span>/09/10 <span class=\"token number\">16</span>:53:33 <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token comment\">#5: *1 open() \"/usr/share/nginx/html/favicon.ico\" failed (2: No such file or directory), client: 192.168.239.1, server: localhost, request: \"GET /favicon.ico HTTP/1.1\", host: \"192.168.239.130\", referrer: \"http://192.168.239.130/\"</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"18\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">192.168</span>.239.1 - - <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span>/sep/2022:16:53:33 +0000<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"GET /favicon.ico HTTP/1.1\"</span> <span class=\"token number\">404</span> <span class=\"token number\">571</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"http://192.168.239.130/\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/45.0.2454.93 Safari/537.36\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-\"</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"19\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">192.168</span>.239.1 - - <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span>/sep/2022:16:53:59 +0000<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"GET / HTTP/1.1\"</span> <span class=\"token number\">304</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/45.0.2454.93 Safari/537.36\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-\"</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"20\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"21\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 查看容器 nginx 从 2022 年 9 月 10 日后的最新 10 条日志。</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"22\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> logs <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--since</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"2022-09-10\"</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--tail</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span> nginx</pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"docker安装lamp\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#docker安装lamp\">#</a> Docker 安装 lamp</h2>\n<h3 id=\"安装mysql\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#安装mysql\">#</a> 安装 MySQL</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>搜索镜像</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> search mariadb</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>下载镜像</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> pull docker.io/mariadb</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>创建并启动 MySQL 容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-d</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--name</span> mariadb <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-p</span> <span class=\"token number\">3306</span>:3306 <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-e</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'你的mysql密码'</span> docker.io/mariadb</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>访问测试 进入到容器内部</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-it</span> mariadb <span class=\"token function\">bash</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>连接 mysql 数据库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>mysql <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-uroot</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-p</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>授权主机访问</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO <span class=\"token string\">'root'</span>@<span class=\"token string\">'%'</span> IDENTIFIED BY <span class=\"token string\">'你的mysql密码'</span> WITH GRANT OPTION<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>刷新权限</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>FLUSH PRIVILEGES<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111547048.png\" alt=\"image-20220911154727633\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111548532.png\" alt=\"image-20220911154801378\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111548774.png\" alt=\"image-20220911154832425\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111549949.png\" alt=\"image-20220911154951790\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111550025.png\" alt=\"image-20220911155030823\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111552275.png\" alt=\"image-20220911155257060\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111553252.png\" alt=\"image-20220911155313149\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"安装php-and-apache\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#安装php-and-apache\">#</a> 安装 PHP AND Apache</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>搜索镜像</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> search php</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>下载镜像</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> pull php:7.2-apache</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>创建并启动 PHP 容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> /opt/php</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> run <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-d</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--name</span> php <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-p</span> <span class=\"token number\">80</span>:80 <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span> /opt/php:/var/www/html php:7.2-apache</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>访问测试</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">vim</span> /opt/php/index.php</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>?php</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>phpinfo<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>进入容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-it</span> php /bin/bash</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>安装 mysql 扩展</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> /usr/local/bin</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>./docker-php-ext-install pdo_mysql</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>./docker-php-ext-install mysqli</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>重启容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">docker</span> restart 容器ID</pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>\n<p>检查 mysql 连接</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">rm</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-rf</span> /opt/php/index.php</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">vim</span> /opt/php/index.php</pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class=\"highlight php\"><figcaption data-lang=\"PHP\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token variable\">$servername</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"mariadb容器的IP\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token variable\">$username</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"username\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token variable\">$password</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"password\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre> </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">// 创建连接</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token variable\">$conn</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">mysqli</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$servername</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$username</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$password</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre> </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">// 检测连接</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$conn</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token property\">connect_error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token keyword\">die</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"连接失败: \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">.</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$conn</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token property\">connect_error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span> </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string double-quoted-string\">\"连接成功\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"14\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token delimiter important\">?></span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111620935.png\" alt=\"image-20220911162029622\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111622443.png\" alt=\"image-20220911162207300\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/202209111637416.png\" alt=\"image-20220911163708227\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://wordpress-1258894728.cos.a